If I am not mistaken, that will probably be a standard 6-rib tranny and ran
from about 76 to 79 (unless it was swapped out by someone else).  For more
tranny info check out the earlier discussion thread or visit some of these
links:

http://www.ratwell.com/technical/FAQ.html
http://www.thesamba.com/vw/forum/viewtopic.php?t=143138
http://www.type2.com/library/drivetra/091data.htm
